{{Infobox dungeon |name = P2 Laboratory |image = [[File:P2 Laboratory.png|300px]] |caption = A map of P2 Laboratory. |tokens = 396,500 |location = Unova Route 18 }} '''P2 Laboratory''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Unova]]. It initially has 81 tiles arranged in an 9x9 square, including 9 chest tiles, 21 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile.
